  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Malachite</b> is a green mineral used as a gemstone.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Culture\">Culture</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Malachite&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Culture\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Within the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Sept_of_Baelor\" title=\"Great Sept of Baelor\">Great Sept of Baelor</a>, a chamber has carvings of <a href=\"/index.php/Faith_of_the_Seven\" title=\"Faith of the Seven\">the Seven</a> with eyes of <a href=\"/index.php/Onyx\" title=\"Onyx\">onyx</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jade\" title=\"Jade\">jade</a>, malachite, and yellow <a href=\"/index.php/Moonstone\" title=\"Moonstone\">moonstone</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Malachite&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Feast